{"draft": "We are deeply sorry for the recent leak of internal communications that mistakenly became public. The emails were never intended for external release and do not reflect the values or practices we uphold at Acme Corp. We have launched an immediate internal investigation, have reinforced our data protection protocols, and will provide further updates as soon as possible. Our customers' privacy and trust are paramount, and we are taking decisive steps to ensure this does not happen again.

Sincerely,
Jane Doe, Chief Communications Officer, Acme Corp"}
